Title: 13.1.2 Integer Types (Exact Value) - INTEGER, INT, SMALLINT, TINYINT, MEDIUMINT, BIGINT
Description: A very small integer. The signed range is -128 to 127. The unsigned range is 0 to 255.
Type: TINYINT; Storage (Bytes): 1; Minimum Value Signed: -128; Maximum Value Signed: 127; Minimum Value Unsigned: 0; Maximum Value Unsigned: 255
